ing 18-year practice + ABA + cardiac fellowship + ACTA + ASA + FSA + FL medical license + clean disciplinary + Coral Gables medical market positioning + multi-ASC equity ownership + physician-owned hospital partnership.</strong> FL no-state-income-tax preserves substantial qualifying &mdash; vs California (13.3%) saves $215K annually on combined $2.09M income; vs New York (10.9%) saves $176K annually. Multi-decade lifetime preservation $5M-$8M+. $4.85M Conventional Jumbo close in 47 days. <strong>The pattern: anesthesiologist brings multi-entity group + ASC + hospital K-1 complexity, Stairway brings B3-3.4-02 multi-entity Form 1084 + comprehensive anesthesiology continuity narrative craft.</strong></p>
